    <h2>Conscious Living Framework</h2>
    
    <div class="framework-level">
      <h3>BE</h3>
      <p>Poles: Agency ↔ Self-Awareness</p>
      <p>Trifecta: Focus / Mindfulness / Presence</p>
      <p><em>Controls quality of consciousness itself</em></p>
    </div>

    <div class="framework-level">
      <h3>BECOME</h3>
      <p>Poles: Ideal ↔ Meaning</p>
      <p>Trifecta: Order / Chaos / Equilibrium</p>
      <p><em>Manages transformation through compression/entropy/cycles</em></p>
    </div>

    <div class="framework-level">
      <h3>CHANGE</h3>
      <p>Poles: Build ↔ Flow</p>
      <p>Trifecta (applies to both information and energy):</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Store: Memory / State / Knowledge / Quantities</li>
        <li>Express: Competence / Ability / Skills / Functions</li>
        <li>Personality: Interest / Trait / Attitude / Qualities</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="framework-level">
      <h3>DO</h3>
      <p>Poles: Moment ↔ Routine</p>
      <p>Trifecta: Goals / Performance / Bottleneck</p>
      <p><em>Manages actual execution</em></p>
    </div>

    <div class="framework-level">
      <h3>PROJECT</h3>
      <p>Poles: Perspective ↔ Strategy</p>
      <p>Trifecta: Platform / Revenue / Assets</p>
      <p><em>Interfaces with external world</em></p>
    </div>

    <div class="framework-notes">
      <h3>Key Features:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Each level has two poles to balance and three aspects that characterize its operation</li>
        <li>Movement between levels is bidirectional</li>
        <li>Levels progress from most internal (Conscious) to most external (Project)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
